Hey Alan,
before you pull the wiper motor--try this.  remove the arms.  remove the 
tiny "Jesus" circlips on the tip of the shafts.  the shafts should 
retract enough to grease with anti-sieze.

I thought I needed a motor but my shafts were just binding.  this was a 
few years ago.

Will A.
So. Lake Tahoe, CA

